        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         When fear kiteing I remove my secondary item and leave the slot empty. I then swap out the fear staff with my Z. heart as needed.</P><P>I use it when:<BR>1) something went wrong and i'm OOM (very rare)<BR>2) fear is resisted.</P><P>When fear is resisted with 2 clicks are are casting it again. Then it's casting time is fine because after the refresh time on fear this is no longer slow. Naturally if i get a resist on it then I try normal fear again.</P><P>not a big deal, but a nice mana saver. It has saved my life a couple times, but that is REALLY rare.</P><P>Then normally sell for more than 6k, so you got a good deal.</P><P>Laeelin</P><P>[<a href="http://www.butterflygifts.net/everquest/images/intheshadows.gif" target="_blank">http://www.butterflygifts.net/everquest/images/intheshadows.gif</a>]<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
