        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I also consider this thing worthless, Im level 52, and if i need 2 fears, i use invoke and regular fear, which i think is 30 mana.</P><P>If invoke fear is resisted, i can cast fear without waiting for invoke to refresh, but I only use this in rare circumstance, I normally dont have 2 fears loaded.</P><P>For people who want this for the look, go to ToFS and get Tserinnas staff, it looks almost exactly the same, and isnt too hard to get, its no drop tho, so you have to earn it</P><P>and for the people who are saying this is saving 100 mana, think of it like this, 7 secs cast time = 7 secs you could be medding, which depending on when you sit and stand, could be 2 ticks.  <BR>I think Lich regens 20 mana a tick, plus whatever normal mana regen is for those ticks, i have no idea the exact number, but thats at least 40 mana you lose by standing and casting, not considering that i regen 12 a tick sitting(i think) as an iksar, so thats hps i lose if i stood up and casted this.</P><P>If you bought it for 6k, you got a good price, considering people usually try to sell it for around 15k, at least on my server, but i would recommend you sell it and you should be able to get at least some of your money back, and use that cash to either, buy other gear, or buy some high level spells, which in my opinion are alot more useful</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
